There is an important feature in <b>RichFaces 4</b> that get documented at wiki recently and today I want to point you to that article. That article is related to <b><a href="http://community.jboss.org/wiki/ProgrammaticControlOfPartialProcessingInRichFaces4" target="" class="regularLink">Programmatic control of partial processing in RichFaces 4</a></b>.
</p>

