</blockquote>

<p class="wikiPara">
 <b>Questions which are adressed in that article</b> (<i>for both RichFaces 3.3.x and 4.x</i>) listed below. Again all the answers related to programmatical access to <b>PartialViewContext</b> and not just working at component/attributes level.
</p>

<ul class="wikiUnorderedList">
